 <metadata>
  <name>New Hampshire -&gt; Harvard</name>
  <desc>Duck into New Hampshire then ride back down the Nashua River Rail Trail (nearly 15 miles of protected bike path!) and then into Harvard before returning home via the traditional route through Concord.</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Tim Beaver</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/23022900"/>
